%% Diagram 03 — GeoProcessor.run satu worker thread
flowchart TD
    START([Thread.start memanggil run]) --> P1[displayProcessingStatus via logLine synchronized]
    P1 --> IO1[/Output: MEMPROSES, Thread ID, getInfo/]
    IO1 --> P2[Thread.sleep delayMs]
    P2 --> D1{InterruptedException?}
    D1 -->|Ya| P3[/Output ERROR + interrupt flag/]
    P3 --> END([run selesai])
    D1 -->|Tidak| P5[hitung luas keliling volume luasPermukaan]
    P5 --> P9[displayResult via logLine synchronized]
    P9 --> IO2[/Output: empat angka hasil/]
    IO2 --> END
